  "author": "Guru Bin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "VA (feliX, voice 1) + Wavefolder (Oscar, voice 2). HAMMER=+0.7 — deep LOVE territory. The reconciliation: feliX's clean analog warmth envelops Oscar's folded harmonics until they fuse into a single voice with impossible tonal richness. At deep LOVE, Oscar's wavefolder harmonics are absorbed into feliX's spectral envelope. The result is something neither could produce alone — feliX wins, but Oscar's character survives inside the victory.",
  "tags": ["ouie", "va", "wavefolder", "felix", "oscar", "love", "fusion", "aether", "reconciliation"],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OUIE — The Hammerhead",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "vol": "Transcendental Vol 1",
    "scripture": [
      "feliX offers warmth. Oscar offers complexity. LOVE makes them one thing.",
      "At HAMMER=+0.7, the wavefolder's harmonics no longer fight — they illuminate.",
      "This is the feliX-Oscar bridge at its most generous: feliX embraces without erasing."
    ],
    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "Sweep HAMMER from +0.5 to +0.9 slowly to find the exact fusion point. Too low and Oscar is still rough. Too high and feliX disappears entirely. The sweetest point is unique to every room.",
    "diagnosis": "Canonical feliX+Oscar LOVE pairing. Wavefolder algoParam2=0.7 creates rich harmonics without crossing into noise. At HAMMER=+0.7 these harmonics lock to feliX's VA fundamental — a genuinely beautiful sonic phenomenon. Excellent for complex pads that read as warm rather than harsh."
  },
